### Sicce Controller (internal Web API)
### Base URL is the Haus application server

@baseUrl = {{$dotenv HAUS_BASE_URL}}

### Get current snapshot
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sicce
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get readings (default limit 100)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sicce/readings
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get readings with custom limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sicce/readings?limit=50
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get device info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sicce/device
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}
